videos.headline: Louisville QB Cunningham drops in TD pass to Fitzpatrick
videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham lobs a 43-yard touchdown pass to Dez Fitzpatrick in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Louisville TE just keeps feet inbounds on big TD play
videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham drops in a pass to TE Marshon Ford, who just keeps his feet inbounds and runs into the end zone for a 42-yard touchdown play.
